data.description: Very charming and inviting single story home located in a quiet subdivision in close proximity to historic Main Street Reedville. Upon entering this home you will notice how it has been cared for and its cozy feel. The open concept floor plan maximizes the available space and with the addition of the screen porch makes it perfect for entertaining or spending quiet evenings at home. Boasting three bedrooms, two full baths, and very low maintenance living makes this home ideal for a first home, second home, or laid back spot for retirement. There is a custom storage shed located in the back perfect for storing toys, lawn care equipment, or using as a wood shop. Also, a large car port to keep a boat or RV out of the elements. Deep artesian well, conditioned crawl space, and new HVAC system installed in 2020 are a few more amenities that add to the stress-free environment of this home. Come see this well built home located in an excellent location and see what Northern Neck living is all about!
